data.description: Welcome to your dream coastal retreat in beautiful Redondo Beach! This stunning home offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and seaside charm, making it a true gem along the California coastline. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the inviting open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and updated kitchen area. Bathed in natural light, this space creates a warm and inviting atmosphere with multiple sliding doors that open up to your private patio that has stunning ocean views. For those seeking an active coastal lifestyle, this residence offers unparalleled convenience. Just steps away from the Redondo Beach Pier, you can easily enjoy beachside strolls, dine at world-class restaurants, or partake in water sports and recreational activities. This property also boasts resort-like amenities that will make you feel like you're on vacation every day. Multiple pools with ocean views, a clubhouse and well-equipped gym are all at your use to elevate your everyday living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Redondo Beach haven your own.
